      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This example delivers exceptional throttle response via its six individual throttle bodies and a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical suite is well-sorted, featuring a recently serviced VANOS system and a documented valve clearance adjustment. Handling is sharpened by a factory limited-slip differential and a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common chassis fatigue. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with a well-loved performance machine, the drivetrain remains robust and the suspension geometry is dialed for spirited apex-hunting. A mechanically sound entry into the M-division's most celebrated era.",
